# Lab Diagram & Design

This document explains the lab topology and network plan.

---

## Topology
- VirtualBox running 2 VMs:
  - Windows Server (Domain Controller)
  - Windows 10 (Client)

Both VMs use two network adapters:
- Adapter 1: NAT (Internet)
- Adapter 2: Host-Only (Internal lab network)

